{"tid":2405392,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[TVB] 到此一遊[粵]    ","createTime":"2021-02-12T10:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T12:08:35.000Z","uid":38456,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b1404bf497351e34f8ded0f952d53c73aaa7e518","tid":2405392,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T10:15:43.000Z","msg":"到此一遊[粵]&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n金牛報喜，邵珮詩、余思霆帶來台灣新春「食買玩」情報。南門中繼市場某熟食店被譽為「天下第一攤」，「冰糖蓮藕」、「心太軟」等美食更是當地人最愛的賀年美食。適逢士多啤梨盛產季節，兩位美女深入農莊，即採即吃新鮮士多啤梨；再到烏來人氣主題湯屋，變身鍋物浸泡「人體火鍋」溫泉，好過癮！迪化街是過年必逛的復古街道，除了乾果，還要選購應節年糕，一嚐傳統好滋味。過節怎少得一頓豐富盛宴，和牛、海鮮火鍋大餐有多豪氣？"},{"pid":"9b63700ecd937e11132f9478745887bc6ea9c216","tid":2405392,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T13:46:29.000Z","msg":"邵珮詩 肥左反而仲靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d12708c689302ba7800154ecd8699bfa63618f7","tid":2405392,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T15:02:07.000Z","msg":"手"},{"pid":"d3a834915fc58248d02b47e88d17c6b49c64ccf7","tid":2405392,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b63700ecd937e11132f9478745887bc6ea9c216","tid":2405392,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T13:46:29.000Z","msg":"邵珮詩 肥左反而仲靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T15:02:23.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"d91c6afaa23a4df48ce4c2c76416427d8b446dd2","tid":2405392,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T15:20:45.000Z","msg":"余思婷勁撚正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6173f7f3ab7de1319e0ac676119634ef8e756c30","tid":